Package: Apollonius
Title: 2D Apollonius Graphs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Stéphane", "Laurent", , "laurent_step@outlook.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computation of the Apollonius diagram of given 2D points and
    its dual the Apollonius diagram, also known as the additively weighted
    Voronoï diagram.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/stla/Apollonius
